Introduction

Julie Han is a South Korean-American rapper, dancer, singer-songwriter, composer, and choreographer under S2 Entertainment.

She is best known as the leader, main rapper, lead dancer, and the oldest member of the girl group KISS OF LIFE.

On May 17, 2023, Julie was revealed as the third member of KISS OF LIFE. The group officially debuted on July 5th, 2023, with their self-titled mini album "KISS OF LIFE".
